      "width": 184, "height": 200,
      "text": "ingest.v1 envelope\n────────────────\nschema_version: \"ingest.v1\"\nsource:\n  channel: telegram\n  provider: telegram\n  endpoint_identity: str\nevent:\n  external_event_id: str\n  external_thread_id: str\n  observed_at: datetime\nsender:\n  identity: str\npayload:\n  raw: dict | None\n  normalized_text: str\n  attachments: [...]\ncontrol:\n  idempotency_key: str\n  policy_tier: enum\n  ingestion_tier: enum",
